# RHCSA Certification Overview

## Full Form

RHCSA = Red Hat Certified System Administrator

## Exam Code

EX200

## Exam Type

* 100% Practical Exam
* Hands-on Lab Based
* No Multiple Choice Questions

## Evaluation Method

The examiner checks:

* Final system state
* Task completion
* Correct configuration

The method used is not important.

The final result is important.

