# RHEL 7 vs RHEL 8

| Feature              | RHEL 7            | RHEL 8                 |
| -------------------- | ----------------- | ---------------------- |
| Kernel               | 3.x               | 4.x and above          |
| Package Manager      | Yum               | DNF                    |
| Time Synchronization | NTP               | Chrony                 |
| Firewall             | iptables          | nftables and firewalld |
| Repositories         | Single Repository | BaseOS and AppStream   |
| Containers           | Docker            | Podman                 |
| Web Console          | Limited           | Cockpit Included       |
| Memory Support       | Lower             | Up to 4 TB             |

